Package: doomrunner
Version: ${VERSION}
Section: games
Priority: optional
Architecture: ${ARCH}
Depends: libqt6core6t64 | libqt6core6, libqt6gui6, libqt6widgets6, libqt6network6, libminizip1
Maintainer: Jan Broz <youda008@gmail.com>
Description: A graphical preset-based launcher for Doom source ports
 Doom Runner is a launcher for common Doom source ports (like GZDoom,
 Zandronum, Crispy Doom, PrBoom, ...) with a graphical user interface.
 It is designed around the idea of presets for various multi-file
 modifications to allow one-click switching between them.
